author: mturyn
msg: Backtracked debugging: it works a lot better by accumulating a list of files to load and then laoding them just before the <HEAD/> element closes, rather than loading them as they come.
Added xap.util.Debug.preloadDebuggables, which loads debuggables and sets xap.util.Debug.preloaded==true, so we can tell if we've already loaded the ones we'll initially expect.
